{"data":[{"name":"88:1","price":"1. ¿Has oído la noticia del Día Abrumador (de la Resurrección que cubrirá a todos los hombres con su horror, ¡oh, Muhammad!)?","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡغَٰشِيَةِ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5968,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"hal atāka ḥadīthu al-ghāshiyati ","translations":["Has","(there) come to you","(the) news","(of) the Overwhelming","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["hal","atāka","ḥadīthu","al-ghāshiyati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1200],[3,1200,2050],[4,2050,3925]]}},{"name":"88:2","price":"2. Ese día habrá rostros humillados,","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ خَٰشِعَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5969,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wujūhun yawma-idhin khāshiʿatun ","translations":["Faces","that Day","(will be) humbled","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wujūhun","yawma-idhin","khāshiʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,3160],[3,3160,4965]]}},{"name":"88:3","price":"3. fatigados por el esfuerzo realizado[1139] (en la vida mundanal),","arabic":"عَامِلَةٞ نَّاصِبَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5970,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1139]  Estas personas serán castigadas porque pusieron su esfuerzo en desobedecer a Al-lah o porque, aunque realizaron buenas acciones, rechazaron la verdad y Al-lah las invalidó.","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿāmilatun nāṣibatun ","translations":["Laboring","exhausted","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿāmilatun","nāṣibatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1210],[2,1210,3985]]}},{"name":"88:4","price":"4. que entrarán en el fuego abrasador","arabic":"تَصۡلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5971,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"taṣlā nāran ḥāmiyatan ","translations":["They will burn","(in) a Fire","intensely hot","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["taṣlā","nāran","ḥāmiyatan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1630],[3,1630,3355]]}},{"name":"88:5","price":"5. y a los que se les dará de beber de un manantial de agua hirviendo.","arabic":"تُسۡقَىٰ مِنۡ عَيۡنٍ ءَانِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5972,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"tus'qā min ʿaynin āniyatin ","translations":["They will be given to drink","from","a spring","boiling","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["tus'qā","min","ʿaynin","āniyatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,1090],[3,1090,2070],[4,2070,3715]]}},{"name":"88:6","price":"6. Su único alimento será de lo más repulsivo ","arabic":"لَّيۡسَ لَهُمۡ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِن ضَرِيعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5973,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"laysa lahum ṭaʿāmun illā min ḍarīʿin ","translations":["Not is","for them","food","except","from","a bitter thorny plant","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["laysa","lahum","ṭaʿāmun","illā","min","ḍarīʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1200],[3,1200,2250],[4,2250,3180],[5,3180,4510],[6,4510,7285]]}},{"name":"88:7","price":"7. y ni los alimentará ni les saciará el hambre.","arabic":"لَّا يُسۡمِنُ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِن جُوعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5974,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yus'minu walā yugh'nī min jūʿin ","translations":["Not","it nourishes","and not","it avails","from","hunger","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yus'minu","walā","yugh'nī","min","jūʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,440],[2,440,1330],[3,1330,1860],[4,1860,2750],[5,2750,3090],[6,3090,6355]]}},{"name":"88:8","price":"8. Ese día habrá (también) rostros alegres,","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاعِمَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5975,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wujūhun yawma-idhin nāʿimatun ","translations":["Faces","that Day","(will be) joyful","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wujūhun","yawma-idhin","nāʿimatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,2430],[3,2430,5635]]}},{"name":"88:9","price":"9. complacidos con su esfuerzo realizado (al ver la recompensa que han obtenido),","arabic":"لِّسَعۡيِهَا رَاضِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5976,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"lisaʿyihā rāḍiyatun ","translations":["With their effort","satisfied","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["lisaʿyihā","rāḍiyatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1300],[2,1300,2965]]}},{"name":"88:10","price":"10. que gozarán de un excelso jardín.","arabic":"فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5977,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"fī jannatin ʿāliyatin ","translations":["In","a garden","elevated","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","jannatin","ʿāliyatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,2200],[3,2200,3725]]}},{"name":"88:11","price":"11. No escucharán en él banalidades.","arabic":"لَّا تَسۡمَعُ فِيهَا لَٰغِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5978,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"lā tasmaʿu fīhā lāghiyatan ","translations":["Not","they will hear","therein","vain talk","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","tasmaʿu","fīhā","lāghiyatan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,1330],[3,1330,2280],[4,2280,3975]]}},{"name":"88:12","price":"12. En él habrá manantiales cuyas aguas fluirán (continuamente).","arabic":"فِيهَا عَيۡنٞ جَارِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5979,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhā ʿaynun jāriyatun ","translations":["Therein","(will be) a spring","flowing","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhā","ʿaynun","jāriyatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,810],[2,810,2400],[3,2400,4174]]}},{"name":"88:13","price":"13. Dispondrán allí de lechos elevados,","arabic":"فِيهَا سُرُرٞ مَّرۡفُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5980,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhā sururun marfūʿatun ","translations":["Therein","(will be) thrones","raised high","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhā","sururun","marfūʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1540],[3,1540,4315]]}},{"name":"88:14","price":"14. de copas servidas a su disposición,","arabic":"وَأَكۡوَابٞ مَّوۡضُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5981,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-akwābun mawḍūʿatun ","translations":["And cups","put in place","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-akwābun","mawḍūʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1340],[2,1340,4005]]}},{"name":"88:15","price":"15. de cojines alineados","arabic":"وَنَمَارِقُ مَصۡفُوفَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5982,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wanamāriqu maṣfūfatun ","translations":["And cushions","lined up","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["wanamāriqu","maṣfūfatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,3005]]}},{"name":"88:16","price":"16. y de alfombras extendidas. ","arabic":"وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبۡثُوثَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5983,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wazarābiyyu mabthūthatun ","translations":["And carpets","spread out","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["wazarābiyyu","mabthūthatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1530],[2,1530,3475]]}},{"name":"88:17","price":"17. ¿Acaso no reparan en cómo fue creado el camello[1140]?,","arabic":"أَفَلَا يَنظُرُونَ إِلَى ٱلۡإِبِلِ كَيۡفَ خُلِقَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5984,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1140]  Al-lah llama la atención sobre la maravillosa creación del camello porque es un animal que los contemporáneos del Profeta —que Al-lah lo bendiga y le dé la paz— conocían bien y podían contemplar. Tiene características que lo hacen único, como su termostato interno para regular la transpiración. La temperatura de su cuerpo puede aumentar hasta seis grados centígrados antes de que el animal empiece a transpirar, evitando así la pérdida innecesaria de agua. Ningún otro mamífero puede hacer como él. La doble fila de pestañas en sus ojos que los protege de la arena, la planta de sus patas, su gruesa piel, su capacidad para estar días sin comer ni beber, etc., hacen que sea un animal idóneo para la vida en el desierto y que no pueda compararse con ningún otro.","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"afalā yanẓurūna ilā al-ibili kayfa khuliqat ","translations":["Then do not","they look","towards","the camels","how","they are created","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["afalā","yanẓurūna","ilā","al-ibili","kayfa","khuliqat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,2740],[3,2740,3130],[4,3130,4050],[5,4050,4670],[6,4670,5995]]}},{"name":"88:18","price":"18. ¿en cómo fue elevado el cielo?,","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ كَيۡفَ رُفِعَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5985,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-samāi kayfa rufiʿat ","translations":["And towards","the sky","how","it is raised","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-samāi","kayfa","rufiʿat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,3240],[3,3240,3810],[4,3810,5175]]}},{"name":"88:19","price":"19. ¿en cómo fueron fijadas las montañas?,","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡجِبَالِ كَيۡفَ نُصِبَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5986,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-jibāli kayfa nuṣibat ","translations":["And towards","the mountains","how","they are fixed","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-jibāli","kayfa","nuṣibat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,1720],[3,1720,2330],[4,2330,3585]]}},{"name":"88:20","price":"20. ¿y en cómo fue extendida la tierra?","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡأَرۡضِ كَيۡفَ سُطِحَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5987,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-arḍi kayfa suṭiḥat ","translations":["And towards","the earth","how","it is spread out","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-arḍi","kayfa","suṭiḥat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1530],[3,1530,2070],[4,2070,3375]]}},{"name":"88:21","price":"21. ¡Exhórtalos (oh, Muhammad)! Tú no eres sino un amonestador.","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5988,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhakkir innamā anta mudhakkirun ","translations":["So remind","only","you","(are) a reminder","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhakkir","innamā","anta","mudhakkirun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,4020],[3,4020,5240],[4,5240,6615]]}},{"name":"88:22","price":"22. No tienes autoridad sobre ellos (para obligarlos a creer).","arabic":"لَّسۡتَ عَلَيۡهِم بِمُصَيۡطِرٍ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5989,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"lasta ʿalayhim bimuṣayṭirin ","translations":["You are not","over them","a controller","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["lasta","ʿalayhim","bimuṣayṭirin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,2310],[3,2310,3945]]}},{"name":"88:23","price":"23. Mas a quien le dé la espalda a la verdad y la niegue,","arabic":"إِلَّا مَن تَوَلَّىٰ وَكَفَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5990,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"illā man tawallā wakafara ","translations":["But","whoever","turns away","and disbelieves","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","man","tawallā","wakafara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1890],[3,1890,3020],[4,3020,4295]]}},{"name":"88:24","price":"24. Al-lah le infligirá el mayor de los castigos.","arabic":"فَيُعَذِّبُهُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلۡعَذَابَ ٱلۡأَكۡبَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5991,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"fayuʿadhibuhu al-lahu al-ʿadhāba al-akbara ","translations":["Then will punish him","Allah","(with) the punishment","greatest","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["fayuʿadhibuhu","al-lahu","al-ʿadhāba","al-akbara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1450],[2,1450,2280],[3,2280,3350],[4,3350,4975]]}},{"name":"88:25","price":"25. En verdad, a Nos habrán de retornar (los hombres).","arabic":"إِنَّ إِلَيۡنَآ إِيَابَهُمۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5992,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ilaynā iyābahum ","translations":["Indeed","to Us","(will be) their return","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ilaynā","iyābahum",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1380],[2,1380,3820],[3,3820,5625]]}},{"name":"88:26","price":"26. Y, después, a Nos Nos corresponderá juzgarlos.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا حِسَابَهُم","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5993,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma inna ʿalaynā ḥisābahum ","translations":["Then","indeed","upon Us","(is) their account","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","inna","ʿalaynā","ḥisābahum",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1320],[2,1320,2750],[3,2750,3910],[4,3910,7165]]}}],"chapter":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah","Chapter Al-Ghashiyah","Ghashiyah","Surah Ghashiyah","Chapter Ghashiyah","Al Ghashiyah","Surah Al Ghashiyah","Chapter Al Ghashiyah","Surah 88","Chapter 88","The Overwhelming Event","الغاشية"],"version":{"key":"spanish_montada_eu","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"es","version":"1.0.0","last_update":1539032400,"title":"Spanish Translation - Noor International Center","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Spanish. published by Noor International Center - was printed in 2017."}}